{"tid":865054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭語錄大整合","createTime":"2018-10-16T16:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:34:21.000Z","uid":216992,"like":114,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"31ffe589b478977ace7c45464b91a53412d65a73","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"持續更新中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>詞語篇</em></span><br />\n1.體諒<br />\n2.準確<br />\n3.客觀<br />\n4.持平<br />\n5. 願景<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>四字詞語篇</em></span><br />\n1.互諒互讓<br />\n2.安然度過<br />\n3.不可推翻<br />\n4.重中之中<br />\n5.言之尚早<br />\n6.一錘定音<br />\n7.暢有成效<br />\n8.預期之內<br />\n9.不盡不實<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>句子篇</em></span><br />\n1.辦法總比困難多<br />\n2.透過呼籲係最有效方法<br />\n3.攞特首出下氣係冇問題<br />\n4.特首係可以比人鬧嘅 哈哈<br />\n5.冇嘢可以強制，你瞇埋眼咪睇唔到囉<br />\n6.我作為一個天主教徒，我每一日都會為香港嘅年輕人祈禱<br />\n7.無人可一生一世<br />\n8.時間過得好快，度月如日<br />\n9.官到無求膽自大<br />\n10.完全可以體會到市民等車好傍偟<br />\n11. 不能不重新考慮我自己的情況<br />\n12. 有好多討論空間<br />\n13. 今日唔踏出一步，過幾年就出現困局<br />\n14.政府係好願意聽市民嘅意見<br />\n15.要有理性討論<br />\n16.唔答呢啲咁無聊嘅問題<br />\n17. 我認為呢個唔係一個數字問題<br />\n18.見慣呢啲激烈嘅講法<br />\n19.唔好太多陰謀論<br />\n20. 呢個係言論自由，總之唔好做啲令人不安嘅事就得啦<br />\n21. 講任何數字俾大家聽都冇意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係憑記憶打出黎 <br />\n如果有漏嘅話 歡迎各位巴絲提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdd1e02199777304e60f6ba08d9cac0bbc3767e","tid":865054,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"有無尊重"},{"pid":"c628bddb63ab2b39baf9867c4dfebe891c00c28c","tid":865054,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"恒大係一間好有potential 既大學"},{"pid":"6373cb3d8e1500fb1cf649a92b7a92ef1c49ab43","tid":865054,"uid":134666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:13:54.000Z","msg":"上綱上線"},{"pid":"4c3bcdd63a947ee463234fb51c35333ea5a95c5b","tid":865054,"uid":134666,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"迎難而上 撼頭埋場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07022451ea427659065b6358d8570d8a0a971896","tid":865054,"uid":134666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4c3bcdd63a947ee463234fb51c35333ea5a95c5b","tid":865054,"uid":134666,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"迎難而上 撼頭埋場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:15:23.000Z","msg":"牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2645549aa0e544e17ab088ba732d007ba03b0373","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fdd1e02199777304e60f6ba08d9cac0bbc3767e","tid":865054,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"有無尊重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢同邊個講"},{"pid":"dd59a53f989cdd8151356f5436e3c9b83c8a5c7d","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c3bcdd63a947ee463234fb51c35333ea5a95c5b","tid":865054,"uid":134666,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"迎難而上 撼頭埋場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1de0ea82823b22099f55ffd0c40da96985efcdc","tid":865054,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b1529f3c35649ea5319378416eedd035a3b5b89","tid":865054,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"重點係，好戲在後頭。林鄭致辭至最後，提及今日係東周刊經典品牌頒獎禮，佢認為品牌要有三個特質：credibility、reliability同與時並進，至於東周刊長遠能否做到，大家「拭目以待」。竟然係「拭目以待」...有在場嘉賓話，單睇兩人發言，已經值回票價。"},{"pid":"34aab4185fba261f9a944412e36f9dcbd4090746","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1529f3c35649ea5319378416eedd035a3b5b89","tid":865054,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"重點係，好戲在後頭。林鄭致辭至最後，提及今日係東周刊經典品牌頒獎禮，佢認為品牌要有三個特質：credibility、reliability同與時並進，至於東周刊長遠能否做到，大家「拭目以待」。竟然係「拭目以待」...有在場嘉賓話，單睇兩人發言，已經值回票價。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451d2dc3da37376c5ca541ea9217d3e21aec9cf1","tid":865054,"uid":89931,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"如果反對我嘅人比支持我嘅人多 我會辭職"},{"pid":"a3d5be29e856e73119cb961b8d196a47e6b3badb","tid":865054,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"香港嘅環境係適合互諒互讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f11ba043529ddd8012d1f08814ffcd79630239","tid":865054,"uid":15815,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"習近平的言行愈來愈有魅力及令人欽佩"},{"pid":"7b2c0b587e555ff082f5fe84cf71dcfabdaa92d4","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>持續更新中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更新版</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-更仔細同清晰細分<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">詞語篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.體諒<br />\n2.準確<br />\n3.客觀<br />\n4.持平<br />\n5.願景<br />\n6.新思維<br />\n7.有決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">四字詞語篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.互諒互讓<br />\n2.安然度過<br />\n3.不可推翻<br />\n4.重中之中<br />\n5.言之尚早<br />\n6.一錘定音<br />\n7.暢有成效<br />\n8.預期之內<br />\n9.不盡不實<br />\n10.開放態度<br />\n11.迎難而上<br />\n12.上綱上線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">句子篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.辦法總比困難多<br />\n2.透過呼籲係最有效方法<br />\n3.無人可一生一世<br />\n4.時間過得好快，度月如日<br />\n5.官到無求膽自大<br />\n6.我認為呢個唔係一個數字問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">社會篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.有好多討論空間<br />\n2.今日唔踏出一步，過幾年就出現困局<br />\n3.政府係好願意聽市民嘅意見<br />\n4.要有理性討論<br />\n5.政府係唔會做傷害市民嘅工作<br />\n6.我有魄力，但唔忍心見到香港社會受傷<br />\n7.唔好太多陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">個人篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.完全可以體會到市民等車好傍偟<br />\n2.不能不重新考慮我自己的情況<br />\n3.如果反對我嘅人比支持我嘅人多，我會辭職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">發悔氣篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.攞特首出下氣係冇問題<br />\n2.特首係可以比人鬧嘅 哈哈<br />\n3.冇嘢可以強制，你瞇埋眼咪睇唔到囉<br />\n4.唔答呢啲咁無聊嘅問題<br />\n5.大家鐘意點講就點講<br />\n6.見慣呢啲激烈嘅講法<br />\n7.呢個係言論自由，總之唔好做啲令人不安嘅事就得啦<br />\n8.講任何數字俾大家聽都冇意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">宗教篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.我作為一個天主教徒，我每一日都會為香港嘅年輕人祈禱<br />\n2.上帝叫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">讚賞篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.習近平的言行愈來愈有魅力及令人欽佩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係憑記憶打出黎 <br />\n如果有錯漏嘅話 歡迎各位巴絲提供及指證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"698c90ae53b3c3b5b39a9d816fb50adf035feea3","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d68aabcd4967b9e75d4f1792e22a5e881758e29","tid":865054,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"我好打得"},{"pid":"9b354cd4bf131719f78c70835a4cad6bc629f054","tid":865054,"uid":47352,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"互諒互讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我DLLM呀！"},{"pid":"e1adb694c8570ee78a750a580dfc2e531c00dfa5","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b354cd4bf131719f78c70835a4cad6bc629f054","tid":865054,"uid":47352,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"互諒互讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我DLLM呀！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"有喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305a18ed5b824a7da20bbf7b0dcb3854e49df06f","tid":865054,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:14:52.000Z","msg":"劉明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b3647cb5a7df15c40385acb2d4102ca67b6a2","tid":865054,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"行之有效"},{"pid":"f9ddfa6dc6bb4a90de0edbba81d945151f6dfaff","tid":865054,"uid":4199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"切實可行"},{"pid":"741bc68e6a82280d48f525ef99d0acfa7fea602a","tid":865054,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e9b3647cb5a7df15c40385acb2d4102ca67b6a2","tid":865054,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"行之有效"},"citedBy":0,"reply