"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2633565cd37066408d71d5d56135d60d89a34dc8","tid":865054,"uid":62321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:11:33.000Z","msg":"仆街有聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"我打出黎嘅時候 不斷有人同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f422b9ebc3d9cd8422ed0f760c070ae3251a14a1","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>持續更新中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更新版</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-更仔細同清晰細分<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">詞語篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.體諒<br />\n2.準確<br />\n3.客觀<br />\n4.持平<br />\n5.願景<br />\n6.新思維<br />\n7.有決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">四字詞語篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.互諒互讓<br />\n2.安然度過<br />\n3.不可推翻<br />\n4.重中之中<br />\n5.言之尚早<br />\n6.一錘定音<br />\n7.暢有成效<br />\n8.預期之內<br />\n9.不盡不實<br />\n10.開放態度<br />\n11.迎難而上<br />\n12.上綱上線<br />\n13.切實可行<br />\n14.行之有效<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">句子篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.辦法總比困難多<br />\n2.透過呼籲係最有效方法<br />\n3.無人可一生一世<br />\n4.時間過得好快，度月如日<br />\n5.官到無求膽自大<br />\n6.我認為呢個唔係一個數字問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">社會篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.有好多討論空間<br />\n2.今日唔踏出一步，過幾年就出現困局<br />\n3.政府係好願意聽市民嘅意見<br />\n4.要有理性討論<br />\n5.政府係唔會做傷害市民嘅工作<br />\n6.我有魄力，但唔忍心見到香港社會受傷<br />\n7.唔好太多陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">個人篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.完全可以體會到市民等車好傍偟<br />\n2.不能不重新考慮我自己的情況<br />\n3.如果反對我嘅人比支持我嘅人多，我會辭職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">發悔氣篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.攞特首出下氣係冇問題<br />\n2.特首係可以比人鬧嘅 哈哈<br />\n3.冇嘢可以強制，你瞇埋眼咪睇唔到囉<br />\n4.唔答呢啲咁無聊嘅問題<br />\n5.大家鐘意點講就點講<br />\n6.見慣呢啲激烈嘅講法<br />\n7.呢個係言論自由，總之唔好做啲令人不安嘅事就得啦<br />\n8.講任何數字俾大家聽都冇意思<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">宗教篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.我作為一個天主教徒，我每一日都會為香港嘅年輕人祈禱<br />\n2.上帝叫<br />\n3.天堂已經預留左位置比我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">讚賞篇</span></em></span><br />\n1.習近平的言行愈來愈有魅力及令人欽佩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係憑記憶打出黎 <br />\n如果有錯漏嘅話 歡迎各位巴絲提供及指證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d7da4a331c6c2c0e1864790261ceca6c45c1b54b","tid":865054,"uid":209701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a273c1eeb50136318f182e5f4c2d63372c1320","tid":865054,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c628bddb63ab2b39baf9867c4dfebe891c00c28c","tid":865054,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"恒大係一間好有potential 既大學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"成日打貪污波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe825a79720b3dd6195cce7e74bc9da55e26b778","tid":865054,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢沉底阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac110d148a6c4ad115c6dbbeb60d8e2eaa4a24eb","tid":865054,"uid":209567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:47:23.000Z","msg